revisions.description: Initial version of this MIB module.

tp8021xAuthMode.name: tp8021xAuthMode
tp8021xAuthMode.description: Select the Authentication Method 0. pap: IEEE 802.1X authentication system uses extensible authentication protocol (EAP) to exchange information between the switch and the client. The transmission of EAP packets is terminated at the switch and the EAP packets are converted to the other protocol (such as RADIUS) packets for transmission. 1. eap: IEEE 802.1X authentication system uses extensible authentication protocol (EAP) to exchange information between the switch and the client. The EAP protocol packets with authentication data can be encapsulated in the advanced protocol (such as RADIUS) packets to be transmitted to the authentication server.

tp8021xHandshake.name: tp8021xHandshake
tp8021xHandshake.description: 0. disable 1. enable Enable/Disable the handshake feature.

tp8021xGuestVlanEnable.name: tp8021xGuestVlanEnable
tp8021xGuestVlanEnable.description: 0. disable 1. enable Enable/Disable the Guest VLAN feature.

tp8021xGuestVlanID.name: tp8021xGuestVlanID
tp8021xGuestVlanID.description: Enter your desired VLAN ID to enable the Guest VLAN feature. The supplicants in the Guest VLAN can access the specified network source.

tp8021xQuietEnable.name: tp8021xQuietEnable
tp8021xQuietEnable.description: 0. disable 1. enable Enable/Disable the Quiet timer.

tp8021xQuietPeriod.name: tp8021xQuietPeriod
tp8021xQuietPeriod.description: Specify a value for Quiet Period. Once the supplicant failed to the 802.1X Authentication, then the switch will not respond to the authentication request from the same supplicant during the Quiet Period. (1-999 second)

tp8021xRetryTimes.name: tp8021xRetryTimes
tp8021xRetryTimes.description: Specify the maximum transfer times of the repeated authentication request.(1-9)

tp8021xSupplicantTimeOut.name: tp8021xSupplicantTimeOut
tp8021xSupplicantTimeOut.description: Specify the maximum time for the switch to wait for the response from supplicant before resending a request to the supplicant. (1-9 second)

tp8021xServerTimeOut.name: tp8021xServerTimeOut
tp8021xServerTimeOut.description: Specify the maximum time for the switch to wait for the response from authentication server before resending a request to the authentication server. (1-9 second)

tp8021xAuthPrimaryIP.name: tp8021xAuthPrimaryIP
tp8021xAuthPrimaryIP.description: Enter the IP address of the authentication server.

tp8021xAuthSecondaryIP.name: tp8021xAuthSecondaryIP
tp8021xAuthSecondaryIP.description: Enter the IP address of the alternate authentication server.

tp8021xServerAuthPort.name: tp8021xServerAuthPort
tp8021xServerAuthPort.description: Set the UDP port of authentication server(s). The default port is 1812(1-65535)

tp8021xServerAuthKey.name: tp8021xServerAuthKey
tp8021xServerAuthKey.description: Set the shared password for the switch and the authentication servers to exchange messages.(0-31 characters).

tp8021xAcctEnable.name: tp8021xAcctEnable
tp8021xAcctEnable.description: 0. disable 1. enable Enable/Disable the accounting feature.

tp8021xAcctPrimaryIP.name: tp8021xAcctPrimaryIP
tp8021xAcctPrimaryIP.description: Enter the IP address of the accounting server.

tp8021xAcctSecondaryIP.name: tp8021xAcctSecondaryIP
tp8021xAcctSecondaryIP.description: Enter the IP address of the alternate accounting server.

tp8021xAcctPort.name: tp8021xAcctPort
tp8021xAcctPort.description: Set the UDP port of accounting server(s). The default port is 1813(1-65535)

tp8021xAcctKey.name: tp8021xAcctKey
tp8021xAcctKey.description: Set the shared password for the switch and the accounting servers to exchange messages. (0-31 characters).

tp8021xPortConfigTable.name: tp8021xPortConfigTable
tp8021xPortConfigTable.description: A list of 8021x port config entries.

tp8021xPortConfigEntry.name: tp8021xPortConfigEntry
tp8021xPortConfigEntry.description: An entry contains of the information of 8021x port config. Here you can configure the ports for the 802.1X authentication.

tp8021xPortConfigPortIndex.name: tp8021xPortConfigPortIndex
tp8021xPortConfigPortIndex.description: This object indicates the port number.

tp8021xPortConfigEnable.name: tp8021xPortConfigEnable
tp8021xPortConfigEnable.description: 0. disable 1. enable Select Enable/Disable the 802.1X authentication feature for the port.

tp8021xPortConfigGuestVlanEnable.name: tp8021xPortConfigGuestVlanEnable
tp8021xPortConfigGuestVlanEnable.description: 0. disable 1. enable Select Enable/Disable the Guest VLAN feature for the port.

tp8021xPortConfigControlMode.name: tp8021xPortConfigControlMode
tp8021xPortConfigControlMode.description: Specify the Control Mode for the port. 0. force auth: In this mode, the port can work normally without passing the 802.1X Authentication. 1. force unauth: In this mode, the port is forbidden working for its fixed unauthorized status. 2. auto auth: In this mode, the port will normally work only after passing the 802.1X Authentication.

tp8021xPortConfigControlType.name: tp8021xPortConfigControlType
tp8021xPortConfigControlType.description: Specify the Control Type for the port. 0. base of mac: Any client connected to the port should pass the 802.1X Authentication for access. 1. base of port: All the clients connected to the port can access the network on the condition that any one of the clients has passed the 802.1X Authentication.

tp8021xPortConfigAuthState.name: tp8021xPortConfigAuthState
tp8021xPortConfigAuthState.description: The authentication status of the port. 0. unAuthorized 1. Authorized

tp8021xPortConfigPortLag.name: tp8021xPortConfigPortLag
tp8021xPortConfigPortLag.description: the lag the port belong to
